"Navigation` sub-menu holds these functions too as well. Refer to the 3D "
"viewport's :guilabel:`View` menu image above for more information."
msgstr ""

#: ../manual/3d_interaction/navigating/3d_view.rst:250
msgid ""
"If you have a wheel mouse, you can perform all of the actions in the 3D "
"viewport that you would do with :kbd:`pad+` and :kbd:`pad-` by rotating the "
":kbd:`wheel`. To zoom a :guilabel:`Buttons` window, hold :kbd:`CTRL-MMB` and"
